data.description: Open Floor plan with privacy wall and no direct rear neighbors. Structural options include extended covered lanai,  master suite with bay windows,  tray ceiling package in home,  and extra windows in master. Beautiful maple auburn glaze 42 inch cabinets with extra large-granite island and under cabinet lighting in kitchen. Additional diagonal tile extended in kitchen,  great room,  den,  bathrooms,  utility room,  and foyer. Gas stub out for pool heater and summer kitchen rough in. This new concierge boutique community with an inspired lifestyle is conveniently located minutes to shopping,  dining,  and entertainment,  beaches and I-75.
